===Specifications=== ====per ''ASUS'''s product page==== * Product Segment: AC1200 (300+867Mbps) * Ports: : WAN: 1x GbE (RJ45 for 10/100/1000 BaseT) : LAN: 4x GbE (RJ45 for 10/100/1000 BaseT) : USB: 1x USB 3.0, 1x USB 2.0 * Antenna: 4x internal PCB antenna * Operating Frequency: 2.4/5 GHz : 2.4GHz 3x Guest network, : 5GHz 3x Guest network * Button: : WPS, Reset, : Power switch, : Wireless (On/Off) * Power Supply: : AC Input: 110~240V (50~60Hz) : DC Output: 12V with max. 2A current * Dimensions 147 x 205 x 66 mm (WxDxH) * Weight: 406g
==Links of Interest== *[https://www.asus.com/event/network/EOL-product/ ''End-of-Life Product List'' on '''ASUS''']
